name: phpMyKey
body:
### phpMyKey
A simple program that requires a one-time-use key to unlock some content.

```
$ cd some_folder
$ git clone https://github.com/KevZho/phpmykey.git
```

### Features
* Admin control panel for running cron, adding and removing keys.
* Single use keys with customized content.
* Easy to use interface.

### Authors and Contributors
Kevin Zhou (@kevzho)

### Support or Contact
Contact [kevzho141@gmail.com](mailto:kevzho141@gmail.com) for help, support, or new feature suggestions.
